{"tid":2121130,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拉莫斯算唔算近年最佳隊長","createTime":"2020-07-23T06:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T13:11:07.000Z","uid":280898,"like":43,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b293e02f83f4dca4beb98c194862b17d28a3562d","tid":2121130,"uid":280898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:20:12.000Z","msg":"功績名望高不在話下<br />\n<br />\n關鍵時刻會挺身而出入絕殺波拯救球隊：歐聯決賽、歐超盃、國家打吡<br />\n<br />\n壓得住班更衣室大佬，c朗摩迪巴爾卻奧斯華拉尼呢啲大粒都服佢<br />\n<br />\n有咩衝突不論場上場下一定衝出嚟幫手，又會睇住班細嘅vinicius,mendy<br />\n<br />\n有出佢同無出佢隊波嘅精神面貌唔同曬，可參考1718歐聯皇對祖兩回合、1819歐聯皇對阿積士兩回合<br />\n<br />\n相反睇某啲隊嘅隊長一逆境就自閉dup曬咁，就發現隊長嘅領導能力對冠軍球隊嚟講好撚緊要，近年有得比吓嘅可能得c朗、佩奧爾、雙特"},{"pid":"80828348c48366d3af4bf02dfc58d2f4478b650f","tid":2121130,"uid":6070,"like":20,"dislike":27,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:21:09.000Z","msg":"軒達臣先係"},{"pid":"15f36cc15e25ced6553a66253c5b44c1d654394b","tid":2121130,"uid":280898,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"80828348c48366d3af4bf02dfc58d2f4478b650f","tid":2121130,"uid":6070,"like":20,"dislike":27,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:21:09.000Z","msg":"軒達臣先係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"領導才能唔差嘅，個人成就未夠囉"},{"pid":"39374f370877f76662ad1c83d08c251a5c59635b","tid":2121130,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"咪又係俾人掃走"},{"pid":"3e956a43178bd6087464f2ac1d89db3dc564dc26","tid":2121130,"uid":280898,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39374f370877f76662ad1c83d08c251a5c59635b","tid":2121130,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"咪又係俾人掃走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:34:43.000Z","msg":"唔影響佢係咪一個好隊長啦"},{"pid":"35b523ce98247fe28dee8b507ab955ed6b51b231","tid":2121130,"uid":61758,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wpGYR96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/